stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> TransactionInProgress: StartPurchase / Refund / Reversal
    TransactionInProgress --> AwaitingResult: Card inserted
    TransactionInProgress --> AbortPending: Abort requested\n(device busy)
    AwaitingResult --> AbortPending: Abort requested\n(device rejected / disconnected)
    AwaitingResult --> Completed: Normal completion
    AbortPending --> AbortPending: Retry on reconnect or state change
    AbortPending --> Completed: Device accepted abort
    AbortPending --> CompletedWithLateResult: Transaction completed\ndespite abort intent
    Completed --> [*]
    CompletedWithLateResult --> [*]